Package: scRDSreport
Type: Package
Title: Reproducible Reports from Single-Cell RDS Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Anbuengsi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "an.bunengsi@qq.com")
Description: Inspects single-cell RDS files, preserves and exports existing
    Seurat analyses, optionally completes minimally processed objects with the
    SCP package, and renders a Quarto HTML report with downloadable tables,
    expression matrices, metadata, and RDS files. Conservative sample-name
    parsing proposes biological groups and replicates with confidence flags.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
